author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Fusion Antibodies Says At Least 40 Pct Revenue Growth Expected​ in FY
text:
March 5 (Reuters) - Fusion Antibodies Plc:
* ‍FOR YEAR ENDING 31 MARCH 2018 AT LEAST 40% REVENUE GROWTH EXPECTED​
* ‍REVENUE FOR FULL YEAR 2017/18 IS BEHIND MARKET EXPECTATIONS​
* ‍CONTINUE TO HAVE POSITIVE OUTLOOK FOR 2018/19 IN LINE WITH EXPECTATIONS.​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
